{"word":"G5104 - τοί - toí - toy - As","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τοί</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">toí</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">toy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">As</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆகிலும் - சொல்லைச் சேர்ந்திருக்கிற துணைக்கூறு, பிற்சேர்க்கை"},{"paragraph":"to undergo, to suffer"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably for the dative case of <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a>; an enclitic particle of <i>asseveration</i> by way of contrast; <i>in sooth</i>: - [used only with other particles in compounds, as <a href=\"#/G2544 - καίτοιγε - kaítoige - kah'-ee-toyg-eh/2544\">G2544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3305 - μέντοι - méntoi - men'-toy/3305\">G3305</a>, <a href=\"#/G5105 - τοιγαροῦν - toigaroûn - toy-gar-oon'/5105\">G5105</a>, <a href=\"#/G5106 - τοίνυν - toínyn - toy'-noon/5106\">G5106</a>, etc.]</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}